<h2>Badge</h2>

<p>This library includes modules related to the badge user element:</p>

<ul class="modules">
    <li><%= DOC.modules.render('Entity/Badge') %></li>
</ul>

<h3>Basic Example</h3>

<p>A badge is generally defined on a span element. However, it may be defined on any inline element based on semantic purpose:</p>

<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;span class="badge"&gt;&lt;!-- Badge Text --&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</pre>
<p><span class="badge">Badge Text</span></p>

<h3>Colored Badges</h3>

<p>The <code>.badge</code> class supports the <a href="#API/Base/Color">Base/Color</a> modules.</p>

