<h3>Alternate Badge Styles</h3>

<p>In addition to the conventional rounded corners applied to a badge, this module also includes a <code>.round</code> class that defines a pill-shaped badge and a <code>.square</code> class that defines a square badge.</p>

<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;a class="badge round"&gt;&lt;!-- Badge Text --&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</pre>
<p><span class="badge round primary">Round Badge</span></p>

<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;a class="badge highlight"&gt;&lt;!-- Badge Text --&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</pre>
<p><span class="badge square secondary">Square Badge</span></p>
